column5: Located in a private neighborhood not many people know about, between 2 fish-bearing creeks in South Austin, only 1 mile from I35, 20 min. from downtown.  Shopping center, 8 min. away, w restaurants- Texas Roadhouse, 3rd Base, Lonestar Steakhouse, sushi, Mexican, fast food, nightclub hotspots- Moontower w live music and outdoor activities. 15 min. from the South Congress area shops, award-wining Texas food! Good for couples, solo adventurers, business travelers, families, and pets.
column8: Southern Country Rm, So Austin-15 min. 2 downtown
